# Source to Docs Sync

When changes are made to the main code in `src/`, update the docs site in `docs/` so documentation reflects actual behavior.

## Required updates

1. Document relevant source changes in `docs/`.
2. If config format changes (new option, renamed key, changed behavior, default changes), update `docs/src/pages/ConfigMaker.tsx`.

## Completion checklist

- [ ] Docs content updated in `docs/` when behavior/spec changed
- [ ] `docs/src/pages/ConfigMaker.tsx` updated when config format changed
